data.description: Drive down your own country dirt road to your new home on acreage! The home is  fully supported by a newly installed solar system with a top of the line Generac Generator for backup. Systems supports whole house, HVAC, Security system and well pump. Fully fenced horse property with plenty of room to build additional buildings. Room for a garden in the front which includes 2 fruit trees and a garden shed with all the needed equipment for the yard. Newly installed flooring, along with newly painted interior throughout. Welcome home! PLEASE SEE EXIBIT A FOR ALL INCLUDED - Property Features & Amenities List
